.faq-box {
  background-color: #EDE8E4;
  border-color: rgba(132,132,132,0.2);
  // padding-left: 30px;
  // padding-right: 30px;
}

.faq-box button {
  background-color: #EDE8E4;
}

.faq-box button i {
  font-size: 30px;
  color: rgba(0,0,0,.5);
}

.faq-box button:hover i {
  color: rgba(0,0,0,.8);
}

.faq-card .number {
  height: 40px;
  font-size: 25px;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.faq-card .question {
  height: 80px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 300;
}

.faq-card .answer {
  height: 150px;
}

.faq-card .number,
.faq-card .question,
.faq-card .answer {
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.faq-box .hidden {
  display: none;
}
<div class="container-fluid faq">
  <h1 class="text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>


  <div class="faq-box text-center row">
    <button type="button" class="btn col-1 col-lg-offset-1"><i class='fas fa-arrow-alt-circle-left'></i></button>
    <div class="faq-card col-sm-11 col-md-5 col-lg-3">
      <p class="number">1</p>
      <p class="question">
        What does your photo coverage includes?
      </p>
      <p class="answer">
        I’ll be with you by the time you are getting ready,
         and we will continue to the ceremony and the reception / party.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-card col-sm-11 col-md-5 col-lg-3">
      <p class="number">2</p>
      <p class="question">
        If we choose you, are you going to be the actual photographer of the
        day? Is there a second photographer?
      </p>
      <p class="answer">
        I’ll personally be your photographer. According to my experience, in
        order to get the best possible and complete result, a second
        photographer, is highly recommended.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-card col-sm-11 col-md-5 col-lg-3">
      <p class="number">3</p>
      <p class="question">
        How much time will you spend with us the day of our wedding?
      </p>
      <p class="answer">
        I will be with you before you start getting ready up to the party.
        I would not leave, if I’m not sure that I have covered every important
        moment of the day.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-card hidden col-sm-12 col-md-5 col-lg-3">
      <p class="number">4</p>
      <p class="question">
        How many photos are we going to receive?
      </p>
      <p class="answer">
        In every wedding I shoot approximately from 1000 up to 2000 photos. You
        will receive all the digital files in high resolution.
      </p>
    </div>

    <button type="button" class="btn col-1"><i class='fas fa-arrow-alt-circle-right'></i></button>
  </div>
</div>



